Package battle

Class AbstractGear

  • java.lang.Object
    • battle.AbstractGear
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Gear, java.lang.Comparable<Gear>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Belt, FootWear, HeadGear, Potion
    public abstract class AbstractGear
extends java.lang.Object
implements Gear
    This is the abstract class gear which implements the gear interface. It includes the fields commonly shared between each gear and different compareTo and equals method to support double dispatch concept.
